BR_text.BRsummary: parseFromFile returns `true` if it failed to parse file.
BR_text.BRdescription:
This code is wrong:
 
 
 
 onnx-tensorrt/ModelImporter.cpp
 
 
          Line 630
       in
       7ec88b9
 
 
 
 
 
 
  return EXIT_FAILURE; 
 
 
 
 
 
 It returns EXIT_FAILURE which is apparently not 0, while function return type is bool.

comments_1.comment_text: Because of this bug, it returns true when the file does not exist... 🙄

comments_2.comment_text: Thanks for the report. Fixed in the above MR.
